      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil half a kettle</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes </strong>(skin on) into thin wedges</p><p>Deseed the <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>roughly</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
