            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>potato wedges</strong> and <strong>sliced pepper</strong> to a large baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until the wedges are golden and the pepper is beginning to char</p>",
