        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the shallot has softened, add your<strong> ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>diced tomatoes</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min</p><p>Add your<strong> tomato paste </strong>and<strong> </strong>100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook for 2-3 min further or until the tomatoes have broken down and the sauce has reduced to a jam-like consistency – this is your <strong>bravas relish</strong></p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1597747497910-x200.jpg",
