    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine your<strong> mayo</strong>,<strong> remaining grated garlic </strong>and most of the<strong> chopped parsley </strong>(save some for garnish!)<strong> </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Add a little splash of <strong>cold water</strong> to loosen, season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby aioli</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
