        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and once the patty[ies] is almost cooked through, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the<strong> ciabatta halves</strong> to the other side of the tray[s], cut side up</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 2-3 min or until the ciabatta is warmed through</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Dress the <strong>salad </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and mix everything together</p>",
